  "2218400": {
    "name": "贪婪大地",
    "steam_appid": 2218400,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款十分爽快的上帝视角roguelike射击游戏，玩家将扮演一名星际佣兵，探索贪婪大地这颗边境星球，拥抱“血腥大地（Crimsonland）+吸血鬼幸存者（Vampire Survivors）”的终极杀戮体验！  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/657cf6bfde2249622d3c20815a670137.poster.avif?t=1771941324\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/657cf6bfde2249622d3c20815a670137.webm?t=1771941324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/657cf6bfde2249622d3c20815a670137.mp4?t=1771941324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/44f21a34b98b72bb9e2854d54753ef9f.avif?t=1771941324\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.0版本正式上线！全新动力甲配合崭新装备及武器，前往未曾踏足的熔岩领域，带给你不一样的杀戮快感！更有机甲模式助你大杀四方！海量内容在此等候。战士，还愣着干什么？马上去军械库报到领取全新动力甲，去杀出一片腥风血雨！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/a3b85bdf272be1330f47bea2225ef755.poster.avif?t=1771941324\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/a3b85bdf272be1330f47bea2225ef755.webm?t=1771941324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/a3b85bdf272be1330f47bea2225ef755.mp4?t=1771941324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/642e2524328c4511a2ced628f6a5020c.avif?t=1771941324\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >排山倒海的怪物向你袭来，弹指一挥间，爆作团团血雾。导弹与火炮齐飞，激光共长天一色！极致的火力输出蒸发你面前的一切敌人。上百万只怪兽分布在数十个关卡中对你虎视眈眈，避它锋芒？直接打穿！用血与火熔铸你的胜利王座！在虚幻5引擎的加持下，极致画面表现力会给你带来一场枪炮齐鸣的视觉盛宴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/7f11f3778f17bd62af8d7582babc13a0.poster.avif?t=1771941324\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/7f11f3778f17bd62af8d7582babc13a0.webm?t=1771941324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/7f11f3778f17bd62af8d7582babc13a0.mp4?t=1771941324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/9d8e2b9572c895ac6ad74babc4bd1485.avif?t=1771941324\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正在等待泰坦降落！被怪兽包围？火力不足？泰坦机甲时刻待命，富有暴力美学的充沛火力，碾碎面前的一切，无论是Boss还是精英怪，不过是路过的“减速带”罢了。钢铁与血肉的碰撞总是令人神往，辅助装备配合机甲升级让你化身移动绞肉机，让怪物们想起被人类支配的恐惧。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/36354cc8e265919d241bd83321286d4b.poster.avif?t=1771941324\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/36354cc8e265919d241bd83321286d4b.webm?t=1771941324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/36354cc8e265919d241bd83321286d4b.mp4?t=1771941324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/cbc9466f652203e567a2f27a95ebc608.avif?t=1771941324\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到军械库！战士！在这里你的火力将得到进一步的进化！每一款动力甲都有着独特的升级，总有一款适合你。各式各样的芯片将助阵你的战斗，搭配300余种升级，最大化提升每一场遭遇的杀戮快感。配合多种辅助装备，赋予了每局战斗独特的体验，更能合成终极装备，助你驰骋“杀”场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/57dd16349c38f38d5ebf6c64459fc759.poster.avif?t=1771941324\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/57dd16349c38f38d5ebf6c64459fc759.webm?t=1771941324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/57dd16349c38f38d5ebf6c64459fc759.mp4?t=1771941324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/694d7d938f3ffe894fdede34356fb3f5.avif?t=1771941324\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还在为一个人打虫感到孤单吗？“我来助你！”在线联机系统正式上线！是兄弟就来杀虫！ 双倍的火力，双倍挑战，超越双倍的满足！还不快带上你好兄弟下来。【现已支持双人在线联机，四人联机功能还在努力制作中！】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/358a0f6a0273377d6e596fdf2554262d.poster.avif?t=1771941324\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/358a0f6a0273377d6e596fdf2554262d.webm?t=1771941324\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/358a0f6a0273377d6e596fdf2554262d.mp4?t=1771941324\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/90875a366c226c29688c7ae15183a67d.avif?t=1771941324\" width=616 height=106 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《贪婪大地》能有今天的成就，离不开每一位支持者！继续聆听玩家们的声音，从玩家中来，到玩家中去，我还会努力持续更新，请保持期待！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2218400/extras/f81e92ebc65991fcc493a553a427c9ae.avif?t=1771941324\" width=948 height=1190 /></span></p>",
